verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Rise up, O men of God!
Have done with lesser things;
Give heart and soul and mind and strength
To serve the King of Kings.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Rise up, O men of God!
His kingdom tarries long;
Bring in the day of brotherhood
And end the night of wrong.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Rise up, O men of God!
The church for you doth wait,
Her strength unequal to her task;
Rise up, and make her great!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Lift high the cross of Christ,
Tread where His feet have trod;
As brothers of the Son of Man,
Rise up, O men of God!{/lang-eng}
